{
  "stem": "2316.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But all of us, all of us, got deathly ill once we started to eat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Boils.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I think-- I think, if I go to a physician right now with any of the boils that I had then, with one boil, whether it was on my arm, my breast, my neck, my butt, my legs, they would have amputated that part.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "That's how bad they were.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were told it's from the reaction, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our bodies just couldn't handle all these foreign things in our system.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were so sick, all of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The entire family bleeding to death practically.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's how it just poured out, all the poisons.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "For months, and months, and months, it was very, very difficult.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, here we have food, and we're not allowed-- we can't even eat it again because we're sick, we're so sick.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we didn't realize that, you know, you start little by little, a little water, a little this.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We just started eating, you know, bread and potatoes-- we couldn't stop-- and vegetables, whatever we could find.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It really made us deathly ill.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we stayed there [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] until-- I don't know how it worked, but I remember we left Kiwerce, and our destination was to get to Poland, to Germany, to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was some organization.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I really don't remember what organization.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe it was the Joint.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a Jewish organization.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Joint took care of us in the camps, once we got there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this was the organization who used to steal refuges through the borders.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came and rescued us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took us through the boundaries.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we traveled to-- to-- we traveled as Greeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
